	<artifactId>mms-application</artifactId>
	<packaging>jar</packaging>
	<name>MMS Plan Schedule Management :: Application</name>
	<description>MMS plan schedule management application.</description>
	<properties>
		<main.basedir>${basedir}/../..</main.basedir>
		<dist.dir>${project.build.directory}/dist</dist.dir>
		<dist.project.id>${project.artifactId}</dist.project.id>
		<dist.project.name>MMS计划任务管理系统</dist.project.name>
		<dist.project.description>
			此服务负责处理MMS的计划任务和邮件发送任务的执行，如果停止此服务，MMS相关系统将无法执行任务计划和发送邮件。
